</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
HVAC control module
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
B1512-H: Air Flow Control Actuator (Position Sensor) and/or Its Circuit Malfunction
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Air flow control actuator position sensor signal voltage is higher than specified value (4.8 V) for specified time continuously.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
